author: Lost in Time
description:
Colorize your own photos (affiliate link): tinyurl.com/lostintimecolors

Today I have colorized and upscaled the best stunts and scenes from the legend of the game, Buster Keaton.

The footage is from these films:
Three Ages (1923)
The General (1926)
Sherlock Jr. (1924)
Day Dreams (1922)
One Week (1920)
Cops (1922)
Neighbors (1920)
Our Hospitality (1923)
Seven Chances (1925)
Steamboat Bill (1928)

I hope you enjoy the video!
title: Buster Keaton's Craziest Stunts and Scenes in Color (4K)
